WEBVTT

00:02:28.116 --> 00:02:31.814
So why did Shalane give up her advantage
to help her opponent win?

00:02:31.838 --> 00:02:33.705
And should you ever do that?

00:02:33.729 --> 00:02:39.896
(Theme music)

00:02:39.920 --> 00:02:43.777
I'm Adam Grant, and this is WorkLife,
my podcast with TED.

00:02:43.801 --> 00:02:46.023
I'm an organizational psychologist.

00:02:46.047 --> 00:02:48.541
I study how to make work not suck.

00:02:49.245 --> 00:02:53.773
In this show, I'm inviting myself inside
the minds of some truly unusual people,

00:02:53.797 --> 00:02:56.998
because they've mastered something
I wish everyone knew about work.

